@DocumentManagementSystem.DocumentService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5255
@DocumentManagementSystem.DocumentService_Bearer = editor

### List documents
GET {{DocumentManagementSystem.DocumentService_HostAddress}}/api/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{DocumentManagementSystem.DocumentService_Bearer}}
Accept: application/json

### Search documents
GET {{DocumentManagementSystem.DocumentService_HostAddress}}/api/documents?search=report
Authorization: Bearer {{DocumentManagementSystem.DocumentService_Bearer}}
Accept: application/json

### Upload document
POST {{DocumentManagementSystem.DocumentService_HostAddress}}/api/documents/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{DocumentManagementSystem.DocumentService_Bearer}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=WebAppBoundary

--WebAppBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Hello from KhawarizMind!
--WebAppBoundary--

### Delete document (replace {id})
DELETE {{DocumentManagementSystem.DocumentService_HostAddress}}/api/documents/{id}
Authorization: Bearer {{DocumentManagementSystem.DocumentService_Bearer}}
